          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1670932680517-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and slice into quarters</p><p>Add the <strong>lettuce quarters</strong> to a bowl with your<strong> cider vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>dressed lettuce quarters</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
